<section id="architecture">
<h2>Architecture</h2>

<p>This section is for developers, integrators, and advanced admins.
Skip it if you only need to grade.</p>

<h3>Adapter pattern</h3>

<p>The single grading UI works against any number of activity types
because each type is wrapped by an adapter that normalises its data to
a shared shape. New activity types can be supported by adding a new
adapter and registering it in <code>adapter_factory</code>.</p>

