<h3>Marking guide save lifecycle</h3>

<p>The save / refresh cycle has to handle the case where the teacher
keeps typing while a save is in flight. The flow is:</p>

<figure class="local-unifiedgrader-help-figure my-4">
<svg viewBox="0 0 800 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Marking guide save lifecycle"
     class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <style>
        .mg-step { fill: #e7f1ff; stroke: #0d6efd; stroke-width: 1.5; }
        .mg-step-write { fill: #d1e7dd; stroke: #198754; stroke-width: 1.5; }
        .mg-step-decide { fill: #fff3cd; stroke: #b08800; stroke-width: 1.5; }
        .mg-text { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; fill: #212529; }
        .mg-text-bold { font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; }
        .mg-label { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; fill: #495057; }
        .mg-arrow { stroke: #6c757d; stroke-width: 1.5; fill: none; }
    </style>
    <defs>
        <marker id="mg-arrowhead" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
            <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#6c757d"/>
        </marker>
    </defs>

    <rect x="20" y="20" width="180" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step"/>
    <text x="40" y="46" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">Type in score input</text>
    <text x="40" y="64" class="mg-label">→ _guideScores[id] updated</text>

    <rect x="240" y="20" width="180" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step"/>
    <text x="260" y="46" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">Focusout (1.5s debounce)</text>
    <text x="260" y="64" class="mg-label">→ _handleSaveGrade()</text>

    <rect x="460" y="20" width="160" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step-write"/>
    <text x="480" y="46" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">Snapshot</text>
    <text x="480" y="64" class="mg-label">_lastSentScores = {…}</text>

    <rect x="640" y="20" width="140" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step-write"/>
    <text x="660" y="46" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">Dispatch save</text>
    <text x="660" y="64" class="mg-label">AJAX in flight</text>

    <rect x="640" y="120" width="140" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step"/>
    <text x="660" y="146" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">Server saves</text>
    <text x="660" y="164" class="mg-label">→ state refresh</text>

    <rect x="380" y="120" width="220" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step-decide"/>
    <text x="400" y="146" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">_renderGuide reconciles</text>
    <text x="400" y="164" class="mg-label">incremental update, per-field</text>

    <rect x="20" y="220" width="240" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step-write"/>
    <text x="40" y="244" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">field === activeElement?</text>
    <text x="40" y="262" class="mg-label">→ keep user's value</text>

    <rect x="280" y="220" width="240" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step-write"/>
    <text x="300" y="244" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">value !== lastSent[id]?</text>
    <text x="300" y="262" class="mg-label">→ keep + re-mark dirty</text>

    <rect x="540" y="220" width="240" height="60" rx="6" class="mg-step"/>
    <text x="560" y="244" class="mg-text mg-text-bold">otherwise</text>
    <text x="560" y="262" class="mg-label">→ apply server value</text>

    <path d="M200 50 L240 50" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M420 50 L460 50" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M620 50 L640 50" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M710 80 L710 120" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M640 150 L600 150" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M490 180 L260 220" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M490 180 L400 220" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
    <path d="M490 180 L660 220" class="mg-arrow" marker-end="url(#mg-arrowhead)"/>
</svg>
<figcaption class="text-muted small">Per-field reconciliation prevents in-flight edits from being clobbered
by the post-save state refresh. The currently-focused field is never overwritten;
fields the teacher has changed since the save fired stay put and re-mark dirty.</figcaption>
</figure>

